<% provide(:title, "Tipjar") %>
<div class="info donate">
	<p></p>
	<h1><%= @infoblock.title %></h1>
	<p><%= simple_format @infoblock.body %></p>
	<%= link_to "edit", edit_info_path(@infoblock.id), class: "btn btn-primary" if !current_user.nil? &&current_user.owner == 1%>
	<h1>Important! Read this!</h1>
	<h2>Currently, the donate button links to <b>Martin Safer's</b> paypal (aka Mount Safurious), NOT Vezley's. If you would like to donate to the creator of this website (Martin Safer), feel free to do so, it would be greatly appreciated.</h2>
	<p>There will be a button to donate to Vezley in the near future.</p>

	<form class="donations" action="https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr" method="post" target="_top">
		<label>Donate as much as you are comfortable with <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-heart" aria-hidden="true"></span></label>
		<label>Remember, this goes to Martin Safer (Mount Safurious)</label>
		<input type="hidden" name="cmd" value="_s-xclick">
		<input type="hidden" name="hosted_button_id" value="DANCDJL8GGZY8">
		<input type="image" src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/btn/btn_donateCC_LG.gif" border="0" name="submit" alt="PayPal - The safer, easier way to pay online!">
		<img alt="" border="0" src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/scr/pixel.gif" width="1" height="1">
	</form>
</div>